
1  Olchani loo sabibu Israel oiu ilng'anayio lenyena. Ore anaa enaponari ilng'anayio lenyena neponaa ashet ilperereni loo lasarri kumok; ore anaa enaponari enkop enye asidanu, neponaa ing'apeta enyena. 
2  Etelejishote iltauja lenye; meeta taata nchere meitalaki entorroni enye. Kegil Olaitoriani lelo perereni lenye loo lasarri, neparripar nena ng'apeta enye. 
3  Amu kepuo taata ninche aajo: “Mikiaata iyiook olaiguanani, amu mikiure iyiook Olaitoriani, amaa olaiguanani, kaa eidim ninye aitaasa iyiook?” 
4  Eiro ninche irorei le pesho; ore too lmuma le lejare keitayu osotua; nebulu nkiguanat enye anaa sayieti naabulu too nkong'at e nkurma.


5  Keikirikira lelo oomanya Samaria te nkuretisho, te nkaraki ilo ashe le Babel. Keishiraki iltung'ana lenyena ninye, ore lelo apolosak lenyena ooserem nkitanyaanyukot neyietu aaishiraki ninye, teina kitoo enye nashomo aing'uaa ninye.


6  Ee kenapi ina toki kewan aaya Asiria, pee eaku enkishooroto te ilo aiguanani kitok. Keitukurruni Efraim, nekurru sii Israel te nkaraki enkitanyaanyukoto enye. 
7  Ore ilo aiguanani le Samaria naa kelo aidaaya, anaa olaburra ti oriong enkare. 
8   Ore nena wuejitin e shumata e Afen, ina ng'oki e Israel, naa keidaikieki. Kebulu ilkiku o laimerrerruani te nchumata lelo perereni lenye loo lasarri; naa kepuo ninche aajoki ildoinyo, Entemoi iyiook, nejoki indoinyo, enturokinoto iyiook.

Eibalunye Olaitoriani endung'okinoto e nkiguana e Israel


9   Ore apa ebaiki nkolong'i e Gibea itaasa eng'oki, iyie Israel; ore teine neshomo ninche aas ing'ok. Ae meinepu ninche olarrabal te Gibea? 
10  Kalotu nanu aarare kulo tung'ana aing'okok pee aitame ninche, naa keiturrurro iloshon aarare ninche, neitame ninche te nkaraki ina ng'oki enye natatashe.


11  Ore Efraim enkashe apa naitamooki, nanyor aidong'o entapa. Naitajeuo apa nanu ina murt enye sidai, kake kalo nanu apik Efraim enchata emurt meeta nchere pee meturisho Yuda, meeta nchere meitupuyiapui Yakobo enkulukuoni makewan. 
12   Entuunoki ate esupatisho, nisampumpu ilng'anayio le nyorrata nauno; entutur ina kulukuoni inyi nayeng'iyeng'ieki amu etabaua enkata naing'orunyeki Olaitoriani, pee etum ninye aeu aitashaiki enjeunoto shumata intae. 
13  Ituuno apa intae entorroni, nisampupu enkarruoisho, inosa intae ilng'anayio le lejare. Amu isiliga apa intae ngarrin inyi o larrabal o ina siamo oo lmurran linyi. 
14  Ore enkaraki ina kejing olarrabal atua iltung'ana linono, ore lelo sempewueti linono neidaikieki, anaa apa enaidaikie Shalaman Bet-arbelon teina olong o larrabal; nedung'udung'i nkera o noo ng'otonye. 
15  Ena ninye eyookini aaitaas intae, iyie na aji e Israel, te nkaraki ina torroni ino kitok. Ore enasirie neishieki ilo aiguanani le Israel katukul.

